  <tutorialSteps>
    <Step>
      <Comment>Intro screen</Comment>
      <DisplayMode>Modal</DisplayMode>
      <Exclusion>None</Exclusion>
      <TargetModeGamepad>MainMenu</TargetModeGamepad>
      <TargetModeMouse>MainMenu</TargetModeMouse>
      <TargetModeTouch>MainMenu</TargetModeTouch>
      <GoalText>Terrain Tutorial (Step 1/3)</GoalText>
      <GamepadText>
        This tutorial will teach you how to:
        1) Add and delete terrain in your world.
        2) Paint the terrain with a new material.

        First, let's start with adding new terrain.
      </GamepadText>
      <MouseText>
        This tutorial will teach you how to:
        1) Add and delete terrain in your world.
        2) Paint the terrain with a new material.

        First, let's start with adding new terrain.
